//spring MVC Configuration - Overview
  1.spring mvc configuration process - part 1: add configurations to file: WEB-INF/web.xml
                                              1)configure spring MVC disatcher servlet
                                              2)set up url mappings to spring MVC dispatcher servlet
  2.spring mvc configuration process - part 2: add configurations to file: WEB-INF/spring-mvc-demo-
                                             servlet.xml
                                             3)add support for spring component scanning
                                             4)add suport for conversion, formatting and validation
                                             5)configure spring MVC view resolver
 
//Creating a Spring Home Controller and View
  1.development process: 1)create controller class
                         2)define controller method
                         3)add request mapping to controller method
                         4)return view name
                         5)develop view page

//reading HTML form data
  1.development process: 1)create controller class
                         2)show HTML form: a.create controller method to show HTML form
                                           b.create view page for HTML form
                         3)process HTML form: a.create controller method to process HTML form
                                              b.develop view page for confirmation
